

@ECHAddress = http://localhost:5202

@port1 = http://localhost:8000

@port2 = http://localhost:8001


### Get cart items (userId = 2)
GET {{ECHAddress}}/api/cart


### Update quantity
PUT {{ECHAddress}}/api/cart/update?productId=5&quantity=56

### Add item to cart
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/cart/add?productId=5&quantity=40



### Q8 - Concurrent checkout (instance 1, same user)
POST {{port1}}/api/orders/checkout?simulatePaymentFailure=false

### Q8 - Concurrent checkout (instance 2, same user)
POST {{port2}}/api/orders/checkout?simulatePaymentFailure=false




### Q8 - Checkout success
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/orders/checkout?simulatePaymentFailure=false

### Q8 - Checkout rollback
POST {{ECHAddress}}/api/orders/checkout?simulatePaymentFailure=true

### ============================================================
### Run two instances (separate terminals) before the concurrency section above
### ============================================================

# dotnet run --urls "http://localhost:8000"
# dotnet run --urls "http://localhost:8001"
